<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Vehicles on Luke Jaeger</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/tags/vehicles/</link><description>Recent content in Vehicles on Luke Jaeger</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://trickfilm.github.io/tags/vehicles/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Late Again (This Bus Goes To A&amp;S)</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/late-again-this-bus-goes-to-a+s/</link><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/late-again-this-bus-goes-to-a+s/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Even death has to wait when the bus is late.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
I built the steel structure in &lt;a href="https://cad.onshape.com/documents/0d04830c3e9a07993e9ffff0/w/ef87bed257ce441c68d4160d/e/46adf5aa0b4f6faa5964491a?renderMode=0&amp;amp;uiState=69f0e03ddc49c9557dbd93cc"&gt;OnShape CAD&lt;/a&gt;, based approximately on the &lt;a href="https://www.alamy.com/this-green-steel-arch-supports-the-125th-st-station-on-the-new-york-city-subway-irt-1-train-located-at-the-intersection-of-125th-street-and-broadway-image383489306.html"&gt;Manhattan Valley Viaduct&lt;/a&gt;, then manually traced it and laser-cut the holes.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Dream | Paul O'Rourke's Car</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/dream-paul-orourkes-car/</link><pubDate>Tue, 24 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/dream-paul-orourkes-car/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Paul O&amp;rsquo;Rourke, an egyptologist who was also fluent in Latin and Greek, was my middle school English teacher — a job for which he was vastly overqualified.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>My Heart's Bokeh</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/my-hearts-bokeh/</link><pubDate>Tue, 26 Aug 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/my-hearts-bokeh/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Misunderstood lyric of the day.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>2 Figures Dancing On Flatbed Truck</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/2-figures-dancing-on-flatbed-truck/</link><pubDate>Sun, 27 Apr 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/2-figures-dancing-on-flatbed-truck/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Elkmobile (For Amara)</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/elkmobile-for-amara/</link><pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/elkmobile-for-amara/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;My daughter texted me indignantly because the New York Times Spelling Bee puzzle wouldn&amp;rsquo;t accept &amp;ldquo;Elkmobile.&amp;rdquo